{"tid":1580910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"921沙田不了","createTime":"2019-09-19T09:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:38:56.000Z","uid":62369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0138533b52cbc65841e944f6913472c244b20e4b","tid":1580910,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"由班藍絲鄉黑自己on99咁係沙田出下醜啦<br />\n沙田變到元朗咁死城睇下啲人屌唔屌佢地<br />\n分分鐘可以睇到佢地自己人打自己人<br />\n同埋我地去到咪又係比黑社會同警畜夾攻<br />\n<br />\n要去就去屯門遊行同元朗靜坐<br />\n<br />\n[b]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵進我退呀<br />\n所以921沙田不了</span>[/b］<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2EO0MUT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2EO0MUT.jpg&h=57d400f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duspt7E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fduspt7E.png&h=63f036e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73b9fba6d00986dc902f97c1113621d48fc95297","tid":1580910,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5Zq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=7d2d9ad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1c5a4fa40134c4871047b5f46c78a1bd82da3ed8","tid":1580910,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets